va\"]]''', in [[Udine]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Mantova]]\", in [[Udine]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt carri 063.png|25px]] 63rd Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Fioritto\", in [[Cordenons]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 07.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Lancieri di Milano\" (7th)|7th Reconnaissance Squadrons Group \"Lancieri di Milano\"]], in [[Remanzacco|Orzano di Remanzacco]]  (two Leopard 1A2 tank companies and one VCC-2 mech infantry company, disbanded December 1989)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 052.png|25px]] 52nd Infantry (Fortification) Battalion \"[[Alps|Alpi]]\", in [[Attimis]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 059.png|25px]] 59th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Calabria]]\", in [[Cividale del Friuli]], ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-2]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 076.png|25px]] 76th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Naples|Napoli]]\", in Cividale del Friuli, (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 114.png|25px]] 114th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Moriago della Battaglia|Moriago]]\", in [[Tricesimo]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 028.png|25px]] 28th Self-propelled Field Artillery Group \"[[Livorno]]\", in [[Tarcento]], ([[M109 howitzer|M109 155mm]] [[Self-propelled artillery|self-propelled howitzers]])\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico mantova.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Mantova\", in Tricesimo\n** Anti-tank Company \"Mantova\", in Tarcento\n** Engineer Company \"Mantova\", in Tarcento\n\n==== Amphibious Troops Command ====\n* '''Amphibious Troops Command''' ([[Lagunari]]) in [[Lido di Venezia|Venice-Lido]]\n** Command and Signal Unit, in Venice-Lido\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt Lagunari.png|25px]] 1st [[Lagunari]] Battalion \"[[Republic of Venice|Serenissima]]\", in [[Mira, Veneto|Malcontenta]], ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-2