ng|30px]] '''[[Granatieri di Sardegna Mechanized Brigade|Mechanized Brigade \"Granatieri di Sardegna\"]]''', in [[Rome]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"Granatieri di Sardegna\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt carri 033.png|25px]] 6th Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Scapuzzi\", in [[Civitavecchia]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt bersaglieri 01.png|25px]] [[1st Bersaglieri Regiment|1st Bersaglieri Battalion]] \"[[Alessandro Ferrero La Marmora|La Marmora]]\", in Civitavecchia, ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-2]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt granatieri 1.png|25px]] [[1st Regiment \"Granatieri di Sardegna\"|1st Mechanized Granatieri Battalion \"Assietta\"]], in Rome, (VCC-1 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt granatieri 2.png|25px]] [[2nd Regiment \"Granatieri di Sardegna\"|2nd Mechanized Granatieri Battalion \"Cengio\"]], in Rome, (VCC-1 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt granatieri 3.png|25px]] [[3rd Regiment \"Granatieri di Sardegna\"|3rd Granatieri (Recruits Training) Battalion \"Guardie\"]], in [[Orvieto]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 013.png|25px]] 13th Field Artillery Group \"[[Magliana]]\", in Civitavecchia, ([[M114 155 mm howitzer|M114 155mm]] towed [[howitzer]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico granatieri.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Granatieri di Sardegna\", in Civitavecchia\n** Anti-tank Company \"Granatieri di Sardegna\", in Civitavecchia\n** Engineer Company \"Granatieri di Sardegna\", in Civitavecchia\n\n==== Motorized Brigade \"Acqui\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA mot bde Acqui.png|30px]] '''[[Acqui Motorized Brigade|Motorized Brigade \"Acqui\"]]''', in [[L'Aquila]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Acqui Terme|Acqui]]\", in L'Aquila\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg corazzato 09.png|25px]] 9th Armored Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Butera\", in L'Aquila, (two [[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]