y Group (from Southern Military Region assets)\n*** Logistic Battalion \"Puglie\" (from Southern Military Region and Armored Troops School)\n*** Engineer Company \"Puglie\" (from Southern Military Region assets)\n\n==== Mechanized Brigade \"Pinerolo\" ====\n* [[File:CoA of the Pinerolo Brigade.svg|30px]] '''[[Pinerolo Mechanized Brigade|Mechanized Brigade \"Pinerolo\"]]''', in [[Bari]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Pinerolo]]\", in [[Bari]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg carri 060.png|25px]] 60th Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Locatelli\", in [[Altamura]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 009.png|25px]] 9th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"Bari\", in [[Trani]], ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-1]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 013.png|25px]] 13th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"Valbella\", in Avellino, (VCC-1 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt bersaglieri 18.png|25px]] 67th Bersaglieri Battalion \"Fagar\u00e8\", in [[Serre, Campania|Persano]], (VCC-1 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 231.png|25px]] 231st Infantry (Recruits Training) Battalion \"Avellino\", in [[Avellino]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 011.png|25px]] 11th Field Artillery Group \"[[Teramo]]\", in Persano, ([[M114 155 mm howitzer|M114 155mm]] towed [[howitzer]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico pinerolo.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Pinerolo\", in Bari\n** Anti-tank Company \"Pinerolo\", in Bari\n** Engineer Company \"Pinerolo\", in Trani\n\n=== Sicily Military Region ===\n* '''Sicily Military Region''' (R.M.SI.), in [[Palermo]] ([[Sicily]] region)<ref>{{cite book |last1=Franco dell'Uomo, Rodolfo Puletti |title=L'Esercito Italiano verso il 2000 - Volume Primo - Tomo I |date=1998 |publisher=Stato Maggiore dell'Esercito - Ufficio Storico |location=Rome |page=41}}</ref>\n** R.M.SI. Command Unit, in Palermo\n** [[File:CoA mil 